 Blackberry Smoke 鼓手 Brit Turner 去世https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackberry-smoke-drummer-brit-turner-has-died-3596673?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=blackberry-smoke-drummer-brit-turner-has-diedSurej Singh Tue, 05 Mar 2024 04:05:31 +0000 Music NewsNews..CountryRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3596673 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/blackberry-smoke-brit-turner@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/blackberry-smoke-brit-turner@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/blackberry-smoke-brit-turner@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/blackberry-smoke-brit-turner@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/blackberry-smoke-brit-turner@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/blackberry-smoke-brit-turner@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/blackberry-smoke-brit-turner@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 2022年，他被诊断出患有胶质母细胞瘤</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackberry-smoke-drummer-brit-turner-has-died-3596673">Blackberry Smoke 鼓手 Brit Turner 去世</a>后的消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/blackberry-smoke-brit-turner@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/blackberry-smoke-brit-turner@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/blackberry-smoke-brit-turner@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/blackberry-smoke-brit-turner@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/blackberry-smoke-brit-turner@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/blackberry-smoke-brit-turner@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/blackberry-smoke-brit-turner@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>美国乡村摇滚乐队 Blackberry Smoke 鼓手 Brit Turner 去世，享年 57 岁。</p><p> Blackberry Smoke 在社交媒体上宣布了这一消息，写道：“我们怀着最深切的悲痛通知大家，我们的兄弟布里特·特纳已经结束了这一生。”</p><p>据信特纳死于胶质母细胞瘤，他于 2022 年秋季被诊断出患有胶质母细胞瘤。胶质母细胞瘤也称为四级星形细胞瘤，是一种快速生长且具有侵袭性的脑肿瘤。</p><p>确诊后，特纳接受了脑部手术，然后于 2023 年恢复与乐队的巡演。然而，在 2023 年末，他透露自己将不得不缺席乐队 2024 年的演出，并宣布肯特·阿伯利 (Kent Aberle) 接替他的位置。 </p><figure id="attachment_3596697" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3596697" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3596697" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/brit-turner@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/brit-turner@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/brit-turner@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/brit-turner@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/brit-turner@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/brit-turner@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/brit-turner@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3596697" class="wp-caption-text"> Blackberry Smoke 的 Brit Turner。图片来源：Keith Griner/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> Blackberry Smoke 在他们的帖子中继续说道：“如果你有幸在任何层面上了解布里特，你就会知道他是人们所希望见到的最有爱心、最有同情心、最有动力、最可爱的人。 Brit 是 Blackberry Smoke 的真正北方，是制定意识形态的指南针，并将继续指导这个乐队。”</p><p>乐队还表示将在适当的时候分享更多有关安排的信息，并宣布设立一项基金来支持布里特·特纳的家人。欲了解更多信息和捐款，请访问<a href="https://factrelief.salsalabs.org/britturner/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>。 </p>